.SS "char* cfgetsubvers (void)"
.PP
Get Library Subversion Details. 
.PP
The Patchlevel returned by this function should match \fBPatchlevel\fP in the public include file \fBcf.h\fP
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
